    Hundreds of new Amiga messages DAILY from around the entire world! Send
email to users in other countries, whether they are Amiga users, scientists,
students, videographers, teachers, and researchers SUCH AS:

    Dave Haynie - Hardware Designer of the AMIGA 3000
    Michael Sinz - Software Programmer of Kickstart 3.0
    Harv Laser - Amiga Journalist, 3D artist
    George Robbins - Commodore Amiga Engineer
